cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a method for joint estimation of orthogonal planes, their intersection lines, relationship graph, and corners in 3D point clouds. This involves semantic plane detection, local and global scan alignment, robot localization, and grasping tasks, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the extraction of reliable features such as lines and corners, which are related to computer graphics (cs.GR). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.GR, in that order.
